sql:
SELECT ads.ad_text, categories.category_name, ads.budget
FROM ads
JOIN categories ON ads.category_id = categories.category_id;

SELECT ads.ad_text, ads.status, ads.city, clients.client_name
FROM ads
JOIN clients ON ads.client_id = clients.client_id;

external_knowledge:
- Ad volume refers to the total number of ads in each category; 
- Engagement is measured by the total number of clicks and views; 
- Overall performance is the average value of all metric performances.

